Frank,
I''ve been dabbling with DRV the last couple days. I did have a smal=
l success a couple days ago. When did you get your 170 message? 

Attached =
is a very brief communication.  Spirit says "hello" then I say "heyyyy"  on=
 play back it sounds like "hello you"  a couple other times I heard them tr=
y to speak but I couldn't understand them.  I'm also attaching one that I d=
idn't understand right away. Joe is my oldest son.  I got these on 610 AM b=
ut I can't get anything on my stereo the last couple days but clicks and so=
me broadcasts.  I did reverse some broadcasts and got some messages out of =
them, regarding changing my frequency, but I haven't noticed anything diffe=
rent.



  ----- Original Message ----- 
  From: Sumption Frank 
  To: EVP-=
ITC@yahoogroups.com 
  Sent: Thursday, July 06, 2006 4:04 PM
  Subject: RE:=
 [EVP-ITC] Jody



   Speaking of radio, I got a voice that I didn't copy t=
o the computer, that said to listen on 107 mhz, presumably FM. They also sa=
id to "call 70", which to me is the 70 cm ham band, which I do have a rig f=
or. 

   My wife no believe this either, I can see her actually turn off as=
 I start talking ghosts, or the electronics involved. You'd think with her =
close call she would be more interested, but I think the necromonger brainw=
ashing from the doctors is already too deep. Necromonger for lack of a bett=
er term, "our culture of fear of death society", so bozo doctors can get ri=
ch. 



   I have the RVG side of a second micro system working. I don't th=
ink I'll try using the surface mount parts on the next systems. It's a real=
 pain to repair the surface mount boards if a part goes bad, like I had las=
t night.  I can always tell if there's a problem, cuz I'm real reluctant to=
 get started on a problem board, not knowing that there actually is a probl=
em. I drug my feet for almost a month ion this system, or course part of th=
at was due to being tied up with the younger grand son.

  Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] Jody



  I agree but if it is them that are not =
willing to talk that way then there is not much I can do.  I've had luck us=
ing this method.  But I think the warning has to do with skeptics.  Interes=
tingly,  I posted this evp on a message board when I received it back in De=
cember and got a lot of slack from a chic on the board.  She was the bigges=
t Witch (a moderator too), because she did not get any results herself.  I =
honestly don't care, who believes me or not. So this could have been a warn=
ing in regards to her.   BTW, your hubby will be more accepting in time, ju=
st give him time.  Bri is a lot more open, especially after going to that c=
emetery in Ohio. Although, lol he said he would never go with me again.  He=
 has a different belief system then I do, and I respect that.



  Jody



=


  Originally received December 10, 2005-notes below



  My little guy wa=
s using the computer and I thought I'd meditate.. lol but can't find the cd=
 I like so I turned on the radio in my room to use the cd player.. it no lo=
nger works not sure why cause we rarely use it.  So I'm sure this is boring=
 you.  But I got an idea to test with the radio again.  I'm bored housework=
 is done and my little guy is using the pc so he doesn't need me.  



  Th=
ey are telling me that this method is not going to be accepted by the other=
s.  Whomever the others may be.  I had the radio between a sports broadcast=
 and another channel.   I amplified this 50%
